716829f-a.title: Manhattan: Bradhurst Avenue - 152nd Street
716829f-a.text:
Bradhurst Ave., north from West 152nd to 155th Streets. Buildings
shown on the left are Nos. 403-417 Edgecombe Ave. (a top Colonial Park).
On 155th Street, is the slevated vehicular and pedestrian approach to the
Central Bridge across the Harlem River.
March 6, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPIODUCTIONS.
